## Overview
SAMA Sentinel is an AI-powered monetary policy monitoring tool that analyzes
Saudi Central Bank (SAMA) communications to detect hawkish or dovish policy
signals. It extracts text from official SAMA reports, scores them on a
1–10 policy stance scale, and visualizes results alongside key economic
indicators in an interactive dashboard.

Built as a portfolio project demonstrating end-to-end data analytics:
from PDF ingestion and NLP scoring to interactive visualization.

---

## Features
- 📄 **PDF Ingestion** — Extracts text from SAMA press releases and reports
- 🔍 **Policy Scoring** — Keyword-based hawkish/dovish scoring (1=very dovish, 10=very hawkish)
- 📈 **Policy Heat Index** — Line chart tracking policy stance over time
- 📊 **Economic Dashboard** — Inflation, foreign reserves, and SAIBOR alongside each report
- 🎚️ **What-If Simulator** — Oil price shock scenario tool showing simulated policy response

